OL,3,CGuernsey retain Muratti Vase after
OL,4,Cbeating Jersey 2-1 at Springfield
OL,5,CStadium
OL,7,FGuernsey have retained the Muratti
OL,8,FVase, beating Jersey 2-1 at
OL,9,FSpringfield.
OL,11,FAfter ending their eight-year wait for
OL,12,Fa Muratti triumph last year, Guernsey
OL,13,Fhave now gone back-to-back.
OL,15,FSaturday's victory was also their
OL,16,Ffirst Muratti win in Jersey since 2014.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
