CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779214266
OL,3,CGuernsey retain Muratti Vase after
OL,4,Cbeating Jersey 2-1 at Springfield
OL,5,CStadium
OL,7,FJersey dominated the first half but
OL,8,Ffailed to take their chances, the best
OL,9,Fof which came when Karl Hinds was
OL,10,Fdenied from the penalty spot by
OL,11,FGuernsey goalkeeper Josh Addison.
OL,13,FThe inspired keeper kept Jersey at bay
OL,14,Fnumerous times before Matt Loaring
OL,15,Fheaded the visitors in front shortly
OL,16,Fbefore half-time.
OL,18,FRoss Allen doubled Guernsey's lead
OL,19,Fafter the restart, bundling home Will
OL,20,FFazakerley's cross at the back post.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779214266
OL,3,CGuernsey retain Muratti Vase after
OL,4,Cbeating Jersey 2-1 at Springfield
OL,5,CStadium
OL,7,FToby Ritzema quickly halved the
OL,8,Fdeficit but Jersey failed to find
OL,9,Fanother way through sparking Sarnian
OL,10,Fcelebrations at full time.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Channel after the
OL,13,Fgame, Guernsey FA Manager Dave Merris
OL,14,Fsaid: " Immensely proud of that group
OL,15,Fof lads who have just done what
OL,16,Fthey've done.
OL,18,F"I don't think there are enough words
OL,19,Fto say how proud I am of those
OL,20,Findividuals."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779214266
OL,3,CGuernsey retain Muratti Vase after
OL,4,Cbeating Jersey 2-1 at Springfield
OL,5,CStadium
OL,7,FGoalkeeper, Josh Addison said: "I'm
OL,8,Fover the moon. It's a massive thing,
OL,9,Fto win a Muratti, and to win it away
OL,10,Fis amazing."
OL,12,FThe game was marred by some clashes
OL,13,Fbetween fans at the end of the match.
OL,15,FAfter Guernsey supporters rushed onto
OL,16,Fthe pitch to celebrate there was soon
OL,17,Fconfrontation between the two islands
OL,18,Fbefore stewards and Police separated
OL,19,Fthe crowds.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
