OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779214266
OL,3,CGuernsey retain Muratti Vase after
OL,4,Cbeating Jersey 2-1 at Springfield
OL,5,CStadium
OL,7,FTim Pryor, the Chief Executive of
OL,8,FJersey FA said: "It's disappointing.
OL,9,FThe Guernsey fans made a good
OL,10,Fatmosphere but we saw flares coming
OL,11,Fonto the pitch during the game and
OL,12,Fthen it's a minority that have gone
OL,13,Fover to the Jersey supporters and then
OL,14,Fyou're asking for trouble.
OL,16,F"I think in the main you can deal with
OL,17,Fa pitch invasion at the end - it's
OL,18,Falmost expected as long as you're not
OL,19,Fcrossing the line."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
